metadata.name: Super Ape University #1
metadata.description: The SAU - Genesis  is a one-of-a(pe)-kind NFT troupe of 200 unique $uper Ape characters with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum network as an ERC - 721 Non-fungible Token (NFT). $AU is an amalgamation of the Legendary Heroes, and Villains. With over 40 top legendary Apes and 350+ hand-drawn traits under a limited supply of 200 $uper Apes — every APE is like no other — exceptionally unrivalled and worthy to hold, for the years to come!
